name: 𝕯𝖊𝖆𝖉 𝕴𝖓𝖘𝖎𝖉𝖊
description: A representation of overcoming unexpected life changes. When you can't help but see the worst in things. Moments when you wish you knew what to say. Time passing by just becomes a waiting game. There's beauty in almost everything. It's all in how you deal with it over time that determines the outcome. Things may not be good now, but eventually, they will be. They have to be.
